  "texts": [
    "Rather than testing systematic search or strategic planning, these puzzles measure cognitive skills for contextual interpretation, conceptual combination, and reasoning from common experiences.",
    "The following fall under this category.",
    "Riddles utilize clever wordplay and literary devices to conceal answers.",
    "For example, \"What gets wetter the more it dries?\"",
    "obscures the solution of \"a towel\" through metaphor."
  ],
